        <rdfs:label>Arrhythmic-trains-or-bursts-discharge-pattern</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:comment>Applies to the intra-burst pattern: a non-ictal graphoelement that repeats itself without returning to the background activity between them. The graphoelements within this repetition occur at inconstant period.</rdfs:comment>
        <hed:hasHedParent rdf:resource="https://purl.org/hed/tag#Discharge-pattern"/>
